{"tid":301942,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 第6-7代處理器HT被揭發有死機bug","createTime":"2017-06-29T04:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T04:26:32.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a853a0dfada2cb6c453b2d8a2a994c967877b011","tid":301942,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"INTEL 第六代與第七代處理器在啟動超執行緒下，在某些運算處理時可能導致程式或系統出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，造成資料毀損或遺失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，影響所有平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，包括桌面、行動、伺服器、嵌入式裝置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，波及Windows與Linux作業系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static4.ithome.com.tw/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/dsc07535-1_0.jpg?itok=qfFPfRSG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic4.ithome.com.tw%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fpicture_size_large%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2Fdsc07535-1_0.jpg%3Fitok%3DqfFPfRSG&h=b8eaf7db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/115158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F115158&d=DphTVTR6uyxFFSve9JDxt49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7b280930\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/115158</a></div><br />\n<br />\n英國劍橋大學計算機科學學院的開源碼專案OCaml Labs發現了英特爾的第六代（Skylake）與第七代（Kaby Lake）處理器含有一臭蟲，可造成系統不穩定或資料遺失，且影響所有平台，而Debian Linux亦於上周日（6/25）提出警告。<br />\n<br />\nOCaml Labs表示，他們<span style=\"color: red;\">去年</span>就察覺到英特爾Skylake與Kaby Lake處理器出現奇怪的狀態，會造成OCaml編譯器的隨機崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，偶爾會編譯失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，或是執行編譯時指令被困住了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而這些問題都源自於超執行緒（hyper-threading）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，於是他們在今年3月知會英特爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但並未得到英特爾的直接回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">未得到英特爾的直接回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">未得到英特爾的直接回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">未得到英特爾的直接回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過，後來OCaml Labs發現英特爾已在今年的4、5月間悄悄修補了該臭蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只是未通知該實驗室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598fe7c27dcafc16b9ff1ab3123cccb71a6846cc","tid":301942,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:19:44.000Z","msg":"Debian Linux指出，啟用超執行緒的Skylake與Kaby Lake處理器在某些情況下會出現危險的行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，例如應用程式或系統出錯，或是造成資料損壞與遺失等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n此一臭蟲影響了Skylake與Kaby Lake處理器所支援的各種平台，從桌面、嵌入式、行動、高階桌面平台到伺服器等，也同時波及Windows與Linux作業系統。<br />\n<br />\nDebian Linux建議使用者可以透過BIOS/UEFI功能關閉超執行緒功能，即可免除該臭蟲所帶來的困擾。<br />\n<br />\n目前英特爾只更新了支援Linux的處理器韌體（microcode，微碼），尚未更新支援Windows的韌體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而Debian Linux則已更新了部份non-free的Debian版本。"},{"pid":"f267d04aeacbe2e4d90ab25ffeb3689e66194f56","tid":301942,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"Mr.A又贏"},{"pid":"b7e9c074377ee7e0eb9f1d9d7d2ba7da6813262c","tid":301942,"uid":32570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4961f67e2dbde27fbfa100ca5afdbcc1641bc51","tid":301942,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:22:15.000Z","msg":"姐係HYPER THREADING 廢左"},{"pid":"046c8fc91bea1689446fd04559baf1191c9fb251","tid":301942,"uid":23473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"Mac 無事？"},{"pid":"fa1f2083f7b1ada75e36239d11434692fb1d2c2f","tid":301942,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Intel CPU出現微碼錯誤，哪些電腦受影響？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/71895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F71895&d=DphTVTR6uyxFFSve9JDxt49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=230c91bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/71895</a></div><br />\n<br />\n在特定情況下，英特爾（Intel）近年推出的中央處理器（CPU）或會導致當機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，原因是CPU的微碼（microcode）出現錯誤，問題只有在使用超線程（hyper-threading, HT）技術時才會出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n英特爾已經修正錯誤，並推出相關更新，但在安裝更新之前，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要防止錯誤發生的方法只有把HT技術關閉。</span>Debain Linux作業系統已推出相應更新修正問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">微軟Windows的用家則也許要再等一會。</span>一旦微軟推出更新，執行Windows更新就能夠解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n英特爾回覆查詢時表示，他們在今年4月已發現並修正問題，建議用戶定期檢查BIOS更新。根據英特爾的文件，錯誤只會在一個實體核心上的兩個邏輯核心均有啟用時才會發生。英特爾似乎認為問題不常見，只向OEM及主機版廠商提供修正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。科技媒體《ExtremeTech》表示，他們使用的i7-7700K及i7-6700K在過去6個月的測試中均未有發生問題。<br />\n<br />\n今次發現的錯誤，影響到代號為Skylake及Kaby Lake系列的CPU，最新推出的Skylake-X亦不例外，但同樣最新推出的Kaby Lake X則不受影響。"},{"pid":"45eb7d09a930127c4ef0b7be12cb8128714842e0","tid":301942,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWindows 出咗更新fix未？"},{"pid":"664000a91ee47c85cc02bcf60139bdb432e75c82","tid":301942,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"屌 唔怪得之我部電腦成日壞啦仲諗緊係咪死HDD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我裝win7 win10 都成日crash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}